  ${NSD_CreateGroupBox} 7u 60u -13u 80u "Configuring Windows multi-boot menu :"
  Pop $0

  ${NSD_CreateLabel} 22u 76u 210u 13u "Install GeeXboX but skip boot-loader operations?"
